194
00:10:59,260 --> 00:11:00,740
Yes, nip it.

195
00:11:01,740 --> 00:11:02,580
Sister,

196
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:04,300
we'll set out
tomorrow morning.

197
00:11:04,860 --> 00:11:05,820
We'll get out
of this place.

198
00:11:06,470 --> 00:11:07,660
Yeah, sure.

199
00:11:08,020 --> 00:11:09,180
We'll set out
tomorrow morning.

200
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:12,540
Your Highness,

201
00:11:13,460 --> 00:11:14,660
General Su's letter says

202
00:11:15,070 --> 00:11:16,660
His Majesty will arrive
in 3 to 5 days.

203
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:17,900
What about him

204
00:11:18,110 --> 00:11:19,110
